The paper deals with lower bounds for branching program size, which is a topic in computational complexity theory (cs.CC). The paper also introduces and studies graph parameters related to projective dimension, which is a topic in graph theory (cs.DS, cs.CG). The paper uses techniques from information theory (cs.IT) to prove some of its results.
